-- Swisscom Says It May Begin Fastweb Buyout in the Second Week of October
-- Paul Verschuur
-- 2010-09-20T15:52:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/swisscom-says-it-may-begin-fastweb-buyout-in-the-second-week-of-october.html

          
          
             Swisscom AG said it may begin the
offer period for the buyout of minority shareholders of its
Italian unit Fastweb in the second week of October. A prospectus
for the buyout was submitted to the Italian regulator Consob
today, the Swiss company said today in an e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        